Classes in edu.columbia.cs.sdarts.backend used by edu.columbia.cs.sdarts.backend
BackEndException
          A very simple exception class designed to notify classes in the sdarts.frontend that something has gone wrong in the sdarts.backend layer.
BackEndLSP
          An interface representing the back end of the LSP; the wrapper onto the legacy collection.
QueryProcessor
          This abstract class should be used by back-end developers for processing queries, because it embodies the logic the STARTS specification follows.
